_sText:
FEND

Bomb/Defuse Map for Counter-Strike: Source

CS:GO original map creator: Mr. Mcsnoogies
CS:S map port creator: Niko
Navigation Mesh editor: Meurglis3

High-quality port for CS:S of the Release Candidate 1 of remarkable samenamed midsize map from CS:GO by Mr. Mcsnoogies.
This port contains some constructive and visual changes in comparison with the original, which was made for bigger detailing and improvement of the gameplay smoothness.

Story:
   Fend Hospital & Medical Center, located in Washington State near Mt. St. Helens, has been taken over by a organized criminal group.
   The bandits must destroy the evidence of their wrongdoings before it can be seized by the enforcement service.
   The task force need to prevent the implementation of these plans...

P.S. ~ Babe, did you forget to take your meds?
